{"tid":1913432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[整合][底已起] 極醜惡FA為求自保 出賣手足","createTime":"2020-03-06T19:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T11:18:11.000Z","uid":352063,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"05e52997ccd081f722f8f6ea0bf9edfee37447b4","tid":1913432,"uid":352063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T19:10:25.000Z","msg":"馬凱螢 Georgina Ma <br />\n<br />\n呢個賤人本身係First aid<br />\n<br />\n11月12號屯門第1次比狗咬 保釋出返嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B0kyt2n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB0kyt2n.png&h=6926b9fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n11月19號凌晨第2次比狗咬 事後佢喺TG私谷自爆佢為咗自己甩身 篤手足灰 指證13個手足火魔 自己就可以喺保釋期間再次被捕嘅情況下踢保成功<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtRmCWq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtRmCWq.jpg&h=10d7ee47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n篇文睇到最尾幾句 你地可能會有錯覺 以為佢最尾都係冇篤到手足 但其實佢喺保釋期間再次被捕 都可以踢到保出嚟 就係佢出賣手足最好嘅證明 順帶一提佢係好多FA team 嘅黑名單 <br />\nFA大佬s知咩事 佢有冇做金手指 自己諗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1j5rjFf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1j5rjFf.jpg&h=00c6404c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4BcpQNQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4BcpQNQ.png&h=3f6c7939&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電話號碼：+852 9877 6727<br />\n<br />\n地址：沙田 <br />\n<br />\n工作：教游水<br />\n<br />\n中學：嘉諾撒聖瑪利書院<br />\n<br />\nInstagram：hygeorgin._<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2hdt4C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2hdt4C.jpg&h=effd0b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此地無銀三百兩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢ig改名 del fol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但天網恢恢 都係搵到你出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FKecfh4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFKecfh4.jpg&h=f583c7ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTG: @iamsodamnxxx  <br />\n以前個名係Be like 三家姐 改咗做煩膠家姐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wbrUXXF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwbrUXXF.jpg&h=f99042fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">此地無銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家成個account唔撚見埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n認住呢個出賣手足嘅人渣 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88zZ9aY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88zZ9aY.png&h=2c2de0cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7tDFcq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7tDFcq.jpg&h=0b1ae89f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAhthY7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAhthY7.jpg&h=2fd90b55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OYrYFcs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYrYFcs.jpg&h=d39b6a79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1 3 個 手 足 嘅 人 生 <br />\n 斷 送 左 喺 你 手 上 。</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">幫手推 我要全香港人都識得佢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n見到上個PO有人話佢一個女仔驚所以篤灰好正常<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我 屌 你 老 母 啦<br />\n驚就唔撚好出嚟 唔好以為着咗件反光衣 就可以攞光環 6個FA一齊拉 點解淨係得佢一個轉污點證人？唔見另外5個又驚？驚就唔撚好出嚟 咪就係你呢啲偽FA影衰晒真&bull;FA </span></span>"},{"pid":"8d9b81aa1ba77da2204c5c99cf8a66390d0014d3","tid":1913432,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:06:56.000Z","msg":"臭雞"},{"pid":"1e5bc8c76db666f9dadccc108e790f1b1e0c3069","tid":1913432,"uid":265424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T20:24:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfc75680d2b285dda6aa062edc7a1321c95d4b4e","tid":1913432,"uid":328381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-0